      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried talking to people but they just say \"it gets better\" or \"get a new pet\" like it's that easy. it isn't. it feels like there's just this massive hole in my chest where he used to be. what's even the point of trying to fix things when everything just feels so hollow and pointless?",
